com.hotels.styx.api.configuration

Interface ServiceFactory<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - factory product type
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Registry.Factory<T>

    public interface ServiceFactory<E>
    A generic factory that can be implemented in order to facilitate creating objects whose type is not known until read from configuration.
